FILENAME: aim_highlife_v1.bsp
FILESIZE: 4376 kb
DATE RELEASED: 24 August, 2007

CREDITS**: Creds to the Hammer Program

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS**: place in ...\steam\steamapps\(steam username)\counter-strike Source\cstrike\maps

DESCRIPTION**: A decent sized texture map with a variety of combat zones to allow for something new every round.

BUGS: None so far. Spent an hour looking for missing textures and things out of place. Please send an e-mail if you have found something I've missed.
